author: Corridor Crew
description: AI Scams are a very present problem on platforms such as eBay and Etsy, especially during the holiday season. We went ahead and bought some so you can see examples of the type of deceit that you might find online, and explain how you can learn to protect yourself against them.
title: WE BOUGHT AI Scams so You Don't Have To
